#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:2 ec04265c1e8d4267b3811fc322b0da70
msgid "Meshes"
msgstr "网格"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:4 6623452f17a048b6afbec812f16f6092
msgid ""
"A :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` is the geometric and topological foundation of "
"every problem in TensorMesh. It holds the points, the connectivity of one or"
" more element types, and any per-node or per-element data attached to them. "
"Because :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` extends :class:`torch.nn.Module`, you move"
" it to a device with ``mesh.to(\"cuda\")``, serialize it with "
"``state_dict``, and let autograd track gradients through anything that "
"touches its tensors."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` 是 TensorMesh "
"中每个问题的几何与拓扑基础。它保存了节点、一种或多种单元类型的连接性，以及附加在其上的任何逐节点或逐单元数据。由于 "
":class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` 继承自 :class:`torch.nn.Module`\\ ，你可以用 "
"``mesh.to(\"cuda\")`` 将其移动到某个设备上，用 ``state_dict`` 序列化它，并让 autograd "
"追踪通过其张量的一切梯度。"

