#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:132 ede570e0025048a79a4912ad53f80f48
msgid ""
"Notice three things in the real output that the table above does not hint "
"at:"
msgstr "请注意实际输出中上表未曾暗示的三点："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:135 e8334719e87d40fabc66bd51fd595a8c
msgid ""
"``cells`` contains a ``line`` block alongside ``triangle`` — the generators "
"retain the 1-D boundary facets so that :class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler` "
"can integrate over them directly."
msgstr ""
"``cells`` 在 ``triangle`` 之外还包含一个 ``line`` 块 —— 生成器保留了一维边界面，以便 "
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler` 可以直接在其上积分。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:139 9339b037801b42819ea22700b12d9f12
msgid ""
"``point_data`` already carries per-side boundary masks "
"(``is_left_boundary``, ``is_right_boundary``, …) in addition to the union "
"``is_boundary``. You get region-aware Dirichlet BCs for free."
msgstr ""
"除了并集 ``is_boundary`` 之外，\\ ``point_data`` 已经携带了逐边的边界掩码（\\ "
"``is_left_boundary``\\ 、\\ ``is_right_boundary``……）。你可以免费获得区域感知的狄利克雷边界条件。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:142 64921561688646218389b9b2a7a3302d
msgid ""
"The ``gmsh:*`` keys and ``field_data`` are the underlying Gmsh physical-"
"group metadata, preserved on round-trip but rarely needed in user code."
msgstr "``gmsh:*`` 键和 ``field_data`` 是底层的 Gmsh 物理组元数据，在往返读写时会被保留，但在用户代码中很少需要。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:146 e891961a2e6043498ceb8d630a6068a0
msgid "Triangle and quadrilateral discretizations of the unit square"
msgstr "单位正方形的三角形和四边形离散化"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:151 885a4dc92929431d9bab5333df49433d
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_rectangle` produces a tri (left) or quad (right)"
" mesh of the rectangle. Mid-edge nodes (orange) are visible because this "
"figure uses ``order=2``; with ``order=1`` only the corner vertices remain."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_rectangle` 生成矩形的三角形网格（左）或四边形网格（右）。由于本图使用了 "
"``order=2``\\ ，因此边中节点（橙色）可见；若使用 ``order=1``\\ ，则只保留角顶点。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:156 45d3ccb447a34363b58858b7d35b5037
msgid ""
"Smaller ``chara_length`` → finer mesh (and finer means quadratically more "
"points in 2D, cubically in 3D). Use ``order=2`` to get ``triangle6`` / "
"``quad9`` / ``tetra10`` / ``hexahedron27`` instead of the linear default."
msgstr ""
"更小的 ``chara_length`` → 更细的网格（更细意味着在二维中节点数按平方增长，在三维中按立方增长）。使用 ``order=2`` "
"可以得到 ``triangle6`` / ``quad9`` / ``tetra10`` / ``hexahedron27``\\ "
"，而非默认的线性单元。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:162 29d090d8ce79446ca785c6b36e3c52b8
msgid "Composing custom geometries with ``MeshGen``"
msgstr "用 ``MeshGen`` 构建自定义几何"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:164 8e1fb9d514dd471b900d77614f5d6ad3
msgid ""
"When the shape you need is not one of the built-ins but is still expressible"
" as a Boolean combination of primitives — a plate with holes, a domain with "
"mixed element types, a 3-D part with cavities — reach for "
":class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen` instead of writing a ``.geo`` file by hand. It "
"is a thin, scriptable wrapper around the Gmsh OCC kernel that returns a "
"TensorMesh :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` directly:"
msgstr ""
"当你需要的形状不是某个内置形状，但仍可表示为基本图元的布尔组合时 —— 例如带孔的板、混合单元类型的求解域、带空腔的三维零件 —— 不必手写 "
"``.geo`` 文件，转而使用 :class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen`\\ 。它是围绕 Gmsh OCC "
"内核的一个轻量、可脚本化的封装，直接返回一个 TensorMesh 的 :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh`\\ ："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:181 1d17fabe72cc4e81a52c306c0614bcbe
msgid "Hybrid 2D mesh with triangles, quadrilaterals, and a circular hole"
msgstr "包含三角形、四边形和一个圆孔的混合二维网格"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:186 3186108496b04dc38168b6d5748cb90d
msgid ""
"The mesh produced by the snippet above — order-2 triangles on the left, "
"order-2 quadrilaterals on the right, fused along a shared interface, with a "
"circular hole punched out. Orange dots are the interpolation nodes (mid-edge"
" nodes are present because ``order=2``)."
msgstr ""
"上面代码片段生成的网格 —— 左侧为二阶三角形，右侧为二阶四边形，沿共享界面融合在一起，并挖出一个圆孔。橙色圆点是插值节点（因为使用了 "
"``order=2``\\ ，所以存在边中节点）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:191 00863121ecdc4d9b91e4abb2035589c9
msgid ""
"The same API extends to 3-D (``dimension=3`` plus ``add_cube`` / "
"``remove_sphere``), and ``element_type=None`` enables hybrid meshes where "
"different regions use different element types — fully supported downstream "
"because :attr:`~tensormesh.Mesh.cells` is a dict keyed by element type."
msgstr ""
"同样的 API 也可扩展到三维（\\ ``dimension=3`` 加上 ``add_cube`` / ``remove_sphere``\\ ），而"
" ``element_type=None`` 则可启用混合网格，使不同区域使用不同的单元类型 —— 由于 "
":attr:`~tensormesh.Mesh.cells` 是一个以单元类型为键的字典，因此下游能完全支持这一点。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:197 c5ec80c72214480c86e654c17dfa05c7
msgid ""
"A picture catalogue of what :class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen` and the built-in "
"generators can produce — primitives, hybrid meshes, adjacency overlays, "
"field visualizations — lives in the :ref:`mesh-generation-gallery` of the "
"example gallery."
msgstr ""
"关于 :class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen` 和内置生成器能够生成什么内容的图片目录 —— "
"基本图元、混合网格、邻接关系叠加图、场可视化 —— 收录在示例画廊的 :ref:`mesh-generation-gallery` 中。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:202 85e3f47c3e9146638e414d7e1cd25429
msgid ""
"For geometries that go beyond CSG (CAD imports, named physical boundaries, "
"anisotropic sizing fields), drive Gmsh directly and load the result via "
"meshio (see :ref:`mesh-io` below)."
msgstr ""
"对于超出 CSG 范畴的几何（CAD 导入、命名的物理边界、各向异性的尺寸场），可直接驱动 Gmsh，并通过 meshio 加载结果（参见下文 "
":ref:`mesh-io`\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:208 83fcd113621146debd8b60a03e336745
msgid "Per-node and per-element data"
msgstr "逐节点与逐单元数据"

