" 都是完整的 :class:`~tensormesh.nn.BufferDict` 对象 —— 你可以用 ``[...]`` 读取它们、遍历它们，或用 "
"``.to(device)`` 移动它们。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:237 f380f509d48445769743a1854edaaafe
msgid "Boundary identification"
msgstr "边界识别"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:239 4f8eb1b27de849ccadb89f5560ba1587
msgid ""
"The generators all populate ``point_data[\"is_boundary\"]`` (a bool tensor "
"over points), which the convenience property exposes as:"
msgstr "所有生成器都会填充 ``point_data[\"is_boundary\"]``\\ （一个定义在节点上的布尔张量），便捷属性将其公开为："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:247 0ea4b60dfa08405e96601986103fe65d
msgid ""
"Hand-rolled meshes can use either ``is_boundary`` or ``boundary_mask`` as "
"the key — the property accepts both."
msgstr "手工构建的网格可以使用 ``is_boundary`` 或 ``boundary_mask`` 作为键 —— 该属性两者都接受。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:250 7d0b6aa74ec642aca197522a70aec37f
msgid ""
"**Per-side masks come for free.** The 2-D / 3-D rectangular and cuboidal "
"generators (:meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_rectangle`, "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_hollow_rectangle`, "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_L`, :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_cube`, …) also "
"register one ``is_<side>_boundary`` mask per face so you can pin Dirichlet "
"values on a single edge or face without recomputing the geometry:"
msgstr ""
"**逐边掩码免费提供。** 二维 / 三维的矩形和长方体生成器（\\ :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_rectangle`\\ "
"、\\ :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_hollow_rectangle`\\ 、\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_L`\\ 、\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_cube`……）还会为每个面注册一个 ``is_<side>_boundary`` "
"掩码，这样你就可以在单条边或单个面上固定狄利克雷值，而无需重新计算几何："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:267 1496634e40874114bce18473183aae18
msgid "Boundary masks on a rectangle mesh — union and per-side"
msgstr "矩形网格上的边界掩码 —— 并集与逐边"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:272 4d599f6ddb85439094c64a8fcb57f778
msgid ""
"Boundary points on ``Mesh.gen_rectangle(chara_length=0.08)``. Left: the "
"union mask ``mesh.boundary_mask``. Right: the four per-side masks set "
"automatically by the generator, ready to feed into a region-aware "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`."
msgstr ""
"``Mesh.gen_rectangle(chara_length=0.08)`` 上的边界点。左：并集掩码 "
"``mesh.boundary_mask``\\ 。右：由生成器自动设置的四个逐边掩码，可直接送入区域感知的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:277 4cc0d29cf8f2433fbf2b4be4ffe06b35
msgid ""
"For curved domains (:meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_circle`, "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_sphere`, …) or hand-rolled meshes, derive your "
"own masks from coordinates and store them as additional ``point_data`` "
"entries:"
msgstr ""
"对于曲边求解域（\\ :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_circle`\\ 、\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_sphere`……）或手工构建的网格，可以从坐标推导出你自己的掩码，并将它们作为额外的 "
"``point_data`` 条目存储："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:290 83e2301954fc42499b3eccba0abcfd82
msgid ""
"These plug straight into a :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` for non-"
"homogeneous Dirichlet BCs (see :doc:`boundary_conditions`)."
msgstr ""
"这些可以直接接入 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`\\ ，用于非齐次狄利克雷边界条件（参见 "
":doc:`boundary_conditions`\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:297 a4d96e556375496fad29262e5eca4094
msgid "I/O — loading and saving"
msgstr "I/O —— 加载与保存"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:299 85359ead9c154fe383f7730723aea927
msgid ""
"TensorMesh round-trips through `meshio "
"<https://github.com/nschloe/meshio>`_, so any format meshio understands "
"(``.msh``, ``.vtk``, ``.vtu``, ``.xdmf``, ``.obj``, …) is fair game."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 通过 `meshio <https://github.com/nschloe/meshio>`_ 进行往返读写，因此 meshio"
" 能识别的任何格式（\\ ``.msh``\\ 、\\ ``.vtk``\\ 、\\ ``.vtu``\\ 、\\ ``.xdmf``\\ 、\\ "
"``.obj``……）都可使用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:303 b8dcb6cc6c14403e8e1e3af1b3b7fa9c
msgid "**Loading.** From a path:"
msgstr "**加载。** 从路径加载："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:309 3cb92e1852e44acb846508d27fe1a87c
msgid "Or from an in-memory meshio object:"
msgstr "或从内存中的 meshio 对象加载："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:317 fed770f2fdc34cd8adfe752168ad8e92
msgid ""
"The ``reorder=True`` flag is **required when ingesting Gmsh or VTK** data: "
"those formats use a different node-ordering convention for quads, hexes, and"
" high-order elements than TensorMesh's internal lexicographic layout. "
"Skipping it produces silently-broken basis-function evaluations. The built-"
"in generators already handle this, so you only need ``reorder=True`` on "
"external files."
msgstr ""
"在 **导入 Gmsh 或 VTK 数据时必须** 使用 ``reorder=True`` "
"标志：对于四边形、六面体和高阶单元，这些格式所采用的节点排序约定与 TensorMesh "
"内部的字典序布局不同。跳过它会导致基函数求值悄然出错。内置生成器已经处理了这一点，因此你只需在外部文件上使用 ``reorder=True``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:324 2ca7f29e378846d695aac7b4aefeed54
msgid ""
"For a side-by-side visual of the two conventions — TensorMesh's internal "
"numbering on top, Gmsh / VTK on the bottom, for triangles, quads, tets, and "
"hexes at orders 2–4 — see :ref:`node-ordering-gallery`. That gallery is the "
"easiest way to verify which convention a hand-rolled connectivity array is "
"using."
msgstr ""
"如需并排查看这两种约定 —— 上方为 TensorMesh 的内部编号，下方为 Gmsh / VTK，涵盖 2–4 阶的三角形、四边形、四面体和六面体 "
"—— 请参见 :ref:`node-ordering-gallery`\\ 。该画廊是验证手工构建的连接性数组使用的是哪种约定的最简便方法。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:330 a4891142d51b48a898e948e5a2e58606
msgid "**Saving.** Whatever format meshio writes:"
msgstr "**保存。** 凡是 meshio 能写出的格式皆可："

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:337 ee1ba5cea64c465c85fce7c94bfd891a
msgid ""
"For ``.vtk`` and ``.vtu`` outputs, ``save`` automatically reorders back to "
"VTK convention and pads 2D coordinates to 3D — no flag needed. The lower-"
"level :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.to_meshio` returns the meshio object directly "
"if you need custom write logic."
msgstr ""
"对于 ``.vtk`` 和 ``.vtu`` 输出，\\ ``save`` 会自动重排回 VTK 约定，并将二维坐标补齐为三维 —— "
"无需任何标志。如果你需要自定义写入逻辑，更底层的 :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.to_meshio` 会直接返回 meshio 对象。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:344 536f35aae3c14ed29dd30b1c9c014d46
msgid "Inspecting and visualizing"
msgstr "检查与可视化"

#: ../../source/user_guide/meshes.rst:346 dff1b531405443198608a890cfdb25f1
msgid "A quick visual check of a 2D mesh and its solution is a one-liner:"
msgstr "对二维网格及其解进行快速可视化检查只需一行代码："

